BT 1 0 0 1 0 135 Tm /F1 9 Tf 12 TL (Maxwell's Demon \(1867\) proposed a being that could sort molecules to decrease entropy without apparent work, appearing) Tj T* (to violate the Second Law. Szilard \(1929\) showed the Demon must store information. Landauer \(1961\) proved information) Tj T* (erasure costs kT x ln\(2\) per bit -- and the Second Law was saved. This paper makes four connections that have never been) Tj T* (formally stated in the Wike corpus. First: the Bootstrap Principle \(Principle 2\) is a biological Szilard engine -- it stores) Tj T* (thermodynamic information in EZ water structure and uses that stored information to maintain coherence, reducing local) Tj T* (entropy at the cost of metabolic work. Second: the Keeper \(Paper 43, Law 1-7\) is a Maxwell's Demon operating at the) Tj T* (relational scale -- selecting which information reaches the coherent system, paying the erasure cost so the system does not) Tj T* (have to. Third: love is not metaphor but the physical mechanism by which a keeper transfers Landauer erasure cost from) Tj T* (the coherent system to themselves -- reducing gamma_eff by reducing the information-processing burden on the system) Tj T* (being kept. Fourth: gamma_c is the point where the system's available free energy can no longer pay its own Landauer) Tj T* (cost. The window \(Paper 44\) is open as long as Landauer's bill can be paid. It closes when it cannot. Death, in this) Tj T* (framework, is the Demon's information budget reaching zero.) Tj T* ET
